Package com.clarionmedia.infinitum.ui.context.impl

Provides concrete implementations for the UI context framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataEvent
    Concrete implementation of AbstractEvent representing the notion of a "data event", which is the creation, modification, or deletion of an entity.
    SessionProxy
    Proxy for a Session which intercepts Session method invocations.
    XmlInfinitumUiContext
    Implementation of InfinitumUiContext which is initialized through XML as a child of an XmlApplicationContext instance.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataEvent.EventType
    Indicates what kind of DataEvent occurred.
